  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "",
      "text": "The MikroTik CADDY is a dedicated NVMe SSD mounting tray designed specifically for use with the MikroTik ROSE Data Server. Engineered for seamless compatibility, the tray provides secure and tool-free installation of M.2 NVMe drives into the server’s hot-swappable drive bays, ensuring optimal performance and ease of maintenance. Constructed from high-quality materials, the CADDY offers reliable thermal contact and robust structural support, helping to maintain drive stability under sustained workloads. Its precise fit ensures proper electrical and mechanical alignment with the ROSE chassis, allowing for consistent high-speed data transfers. Ideal for expanding storage or replacing drives in enterprise or high-performance network environments, the MikroTik CADDY is a critical accessory for maximizing the functionality and scalability of your ROSE Data Server setup."
    }
